match_context.values: @{EventID=1; Product=Microsoft\xae Windows\xae Operating System; ParentImage=C:\Windows\System32\cmd.exe; FileVersion=10.0.17134.1 (WinBuild.160101.0800); CurrentDirectory=C:\Users\george\Desktop\; Image=C:\Windows\System32\regsvr32.exe; IntegrityLevel=High; ParentCommandLine=cmd /c regsvr32.exe /s C:\Users\george\.edge\estsoftservice.dat; CommandLine=regsvr32.exe  /s C:\Users\george\.edge\estsoftservice.dat; Hashes=SHA1=3B9DD8D84C888DA77EB06CFB43E393DD50E0CE6F,MD5=D78B75FC68247E8A63ACBA846182740E,SHA256=12E08492893DBCE4C120D69205C82C32C1AC556D2C244B3B536018A5A274355E,IMPHASH=0235FF9A007804882636BCCCFB4D1A2F; Company=Microsoft Corporation; OriginalFileName=REGSVR32.EXE; Description=Microsoft(C) Register Server}
@{CommandLine=%WINDIR%\system32\regsvr32.exe; Image=C:\Windows\system32\regsvr32.exe; EventID=1}
